## Your Domain

**Focus area:** {{DOMAIN_DESCRIPTION}}
*(e.g. "AI/ML research", "Android development", "competitive intelligence", "personal finance")*

**Key entity types in this domain:** {{ENTITY_TYPES}}
*(e.g. "researchers, papers, models, datasets" or "people, companies, products, APIs")*

**Key concept domains:** {{CONCEPT_DOMAINS}}
*(e.g. "ml/, android/, architecture/" — determines wiki/concepts/ subdirectory structure)*

---

## Architecture

```
raw/              ← Human inbox. Any file type. You NEVER modify these.
wiki/
  sources/        ← One summary page per raw source
  entities/       ← {{ENTITY_TYPES}}
  concepts/       ← {{CONCEPT_DOMAINS}} and other ideas/patterns
  synthesis/      ← Filed query results and cross-source analyses
  index.md        ← Master catalog (you maintain this)
  log.md          ← Append-only operation log
knowledge-base/   ← Managed by tooling (embeddings, metadata, amendments)
```

---

## Page Format

Every wiki page has YAML frontmatter:

```yaml
---
type: source | entity | concept | synthesis
title: Page Title
tags: [{{RELEVANT_TAGS}}]
sources: [raw/filename]
created: YYYY-MM-DD
updated: YYYY-MM-DD
---
```

Internal links use wikilink syntax: `[[PageTitle]]` or `[[PageTitle|Display Text]]`

